)

254:
WITH bond_elements AS (
    SELECT 
        b.bond_id,
        a1.element AS element1,
        a2.element AS element2,
        CASE WHEN a1.element <= a2.element THEN a1.element || '-' || a2.element
             ELSE a2.element || '-' || a1.element END AS element_pair
    FROM bond b
    JOIN connected c1 ON b.bond_id = c1.bond_id
    JOIN connected c2 ON b.bond_id = c2.bond_id
    JOIN atom a1 ON c1.atom_id = a1.atom_id
    JOIN atom a2 ON c2.atom_id2 = a2.atom_id
    WHERE c1.atom_id < c2.atom_id
),
element_pair_counts AS (
    SELECT 
        element_pair,
        COUNT(*) AS pair_count
    FROM bond_elements
    GROUP BY element_pair
),
max_pair AS (
    SELECT 
        MAX(pair_count) AS max_count
    FROM element_pair_counts
),
total_bonds AS (
    SELECT 
        COUNT(*) AS total
    FROM bond
)
SELECT 
    (epc.pair_count * 100.0 / tb.total) AS percentage
FROM element_pair_counts epc
JOIN max_pair mp ON epc.pair_count = mp.max_count
JOIN total_bonds tb ON 1=1
ORDER BY epc.pair_count DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	toxicology

701:
WITH MostInfluentialUser AS (
    SELECT OwnerUserId, COUNT(*) as PostCount
    FROM posts
    WHERE OwnerUserId IS NOT NULL
    GROUP BY OwnerUserId
    ORDER BY PostCount DESC
    LIMIT 1
),
UserPosts AS (
    SELECT 
        COUNT(*) as TotalPosts,
        SUM(CASE WHEN Score > 50 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as HighScorePosts
    FROM posts
    WHERE OwnerUserId = (SELECT OwnerUserId FROM MostInfluentialUser)
)
SELECT 
    (HighScorePosts * 100.0 / TotalPosts) as PercentageHighScorePosts
FROM UserPosts	----- bird -----	codebase_community

    CASE 
        WHEN p1.height > p2.height THEN p1.player_name
        ELSE p2.player_name
    END AS player_name,
    CASE

        ELSE AVG(pa2.finishing)
    END AS avg_finishing
FROM 
    (SELECT player_api_id, player_name, height FROM "Player" WHERE height IS NOT NULL ORDER BY height DESC LIMIT 1) p1,
    (SELECT player_api_id, player_name, height FROM "Player" WHERE height IS NOT NULL ORDER BY height ASC LIMIT 1) p2
LEFT JOIN "Player_Attributes" pa1 ON p1.player_api_id = pa1.player_api_id
LEFT JOIN "Player_Attributes" pa2 ON p2.player_api_id = pa2.player_api_id
GROUP BY p1.player_name, p2.player_name, p1.height, p2.height
ORDER BY avg_finishing DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	european_football_2

1482:
WITH segment_consumption AS (
    SELECT 
        c."Segment",
        SUBSTR(y."Date", 1, 4) AS year,
        SUM(y."Consumption") AS total_consumption
    FROM 
        yearmonth y
    JOIN 
        customers c ON y."CustomerID" = c."CustomerID"
    WHERE 
        c."Currency" = 'EUR' 
        AND c."Segment" IN ('SME', 'LAM', 'KAM')
        AND (SUBSTR(y."Date", 1, 4) = '2012' OR SUBSTR(y."Date", 1, 4) = '2013')
    GROUP BY 
        c."Segment", SUBSTR(y."Date", 1, 4)
),
segment_growth AS (
    SELECT 
        s1."Segment",
        ((s2.total_consumption - s1.total_consumption) / s1.total_consumption) * 100 AS percentage_increase
    FROM 
        segment_consumption s1
    JOIN 
        segment_consumption s2 ON s1."Segment" = s2."Segment" AND s1.year = '2012' AND s2.year = '2013'
)
SELECT 
    "Segment" AS segment_with_biggest_increase
FROM 
    segment_growth
ORDER BY 
    percentage_increase DESC
LIMIT 1
UNION ALL
SELECT 
    "Segment" AS segment_with_lowest_increase
FROM 
    segment_growth
ORDER BY 
    percentage_increase ASC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

1525:
SELECT 
    (COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN c."Currency" = 'EUR' THEN t."CustomerID" END) * 100.0 / 
    COUNT(DISTINCT t."CustomerID")) AS percentage
FROM transactions_1k t
JOIN customers c ON t."CustomerID" = c."CustomerID"
WHERE t."Date" = '2012-08-25'	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
1526:
SELECT 
  (1 - (SUM(CASE WHEN "Date" LIKE '2013%' THEN "Consumption" ELSE 0 END) / 
        SUM(CASE WHEN "Date" LIKE '2012%' THEN "Consumption" ELSE 0 END))) * 100 AS consumption_decrease_rate
FROM yearmonth
WHERE "CustomerID" IN (
  SELECT DISTINCT t."CustomerID" 
  FROM transactions_1k t
  WHERE t."Date" = '2012-08-25' 
  AND t."Price" = 634.8
)	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
1527:
SELECT g."GasStationID", SUM(t."Price") AS total_revenue
FROM transactions_1k t
JOIN gasstations g ON t."GasStationID" = g."GasStationID"
GROUP BY g."GasStationID"
ORDER BY total_revenue DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

1529:
SELECT SUM(t."Price") AS total_spent
FROM transactions_1k t
WHERE t."CustomerID" = 38508
UNION ALL
SELECT SUM(t."Price") AS january_2012_spent
FROM transactions_1k t
WHERE t."CustomerID" = 38508
AND t."Date" BETWEEN '2012-01-01' AND '2012-01-31'	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
1530:
SELECT p."Description", SUM(t."Amount") AS total_amount
FROM transactions_1k t
JOIN products p ON t."ProductID" = p."ProductID"
GROUP BY p."Description"
ORDER BY total_amount DESC
LIMIT 5;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
1531:
WITH top_customer AS (
    SELECT "CustomerID", SUM("Price") AS total_spent
    FROM transactions_1k
    GROUP BY "CustomerID"
    ORDER BY total_spent DESC
    LIMIT 1
)
SELECT 
    tc."CustomerID",
    c."Currency",
    AVG(t."Price" / t."Amount") AS avg_price_per_item
FROM top_customer tc
JOIN transactions_1k t ON tc."CustomerID" = t."CustomerID"
JOIN customers c ON tc."CustomerID" = c."CustomerID"
GROUP BY tc."CustomerID", c."Currency"	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
1532:
SELECT g."Country"
FROM transactions_1k t
JOIN gasstations g ON t."GasStationID" = g."GasStationID"
WHERE t."ProductID" = 2 AND t."Amount" = 1
ORDER BY t."Price" DESC
LIMIT 1;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

SELECT c."CustomerID", ym."Consumption"
FROM customers c
JOIN transactions_1k t ON c."CustomerID" = t."CustomerID"
JOIN yearmonth ym ON c."CustomerID" = ym."CustomerID"
WHERE t."ProductID" = 5
AND t."Price" / t."Amount" > 29.00
AND ym."Date" = '201208'	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
